{"name":"http-server-cli","version":"0.2.1","description":"A simple zero-configuration command-line http server","main":"./lib/http-server-cli","repository":"https://github.com/yeanzhi/http-server-cli","keywords":["cli","command"],"scripts":{"start":"node ./bin/http-server-cli","pretest":"stylezero bin/ lib/ test","test":"vows --spec --isolate"},"dependencies":{"colors":"1.0.3","corser":"~2.0.0","director":"^1.2.8","ecstatic":"~0.7.0","http-proxy":"^1.8.1","minimist":"^1.1.1","opener":"~1.4.0","portfinder":"0.4.x","request":"^2.55.0","restful":"^0.4.5","union":"~0.4.3"},"devDependencies":{"vows":"0.7.x","request":"2.49.x","stylezero":"2.2.0"},"licenses":[{"type":"MIT","url":""}],"preferGlobal":"true","bin":{"http-server-cli":"./bin/http-server-cli"},"gitHead":"2be8f549923cf1601510a0d8e1412491e047936f","homepage":"https://github.com/yeanzhi/http-server-cli","versions":[{"number":"0.1.0","date":"2015-04-27T14:05:51.449Z"},{"number":"0.1.1","date":"2015-04-27T14:18:55.774Z"},{"number":"0.1.2","date":"2015-04-27T14:25:39.796Z"},{"number":"0.1.3","date":"2015-04-27T14:30:20.181Z"},{"number":"0.1.4","date":"2015-04-27T14:32:15.259Z"},{"number":"0.1.5","date":"2015-04-27T16:05:33.163Z"},{"number":"0.1.6","date":"2015-04-27T16:43:02.287Z"},{"number":"0.1.7","date":"2015-04-28T02:21:43.010Z"},{"number":"0.2.0","date":"2015-04-28T02:34:44.610Z"},{"number":"0.2.1","date":"2015-04-28T06:35:52.356Z"}],"readme":"# http-server-cli\n一个无侵入式的可以mock数据的http server服务器\n\n安装\n```\nnpm install -g http-server-cli\n```\n\n启动服务器\n```\nhttp-server-cli\n```\n\n更多命令输入\n```\nhttp-server-cli -h\n```\n\n***三步***开启mock功能\n##1,创建配置文件http-server-config.js\n```\nmodule.exports = {\n     router:{\n         get:[{\"/getinfo\":\"info.json\"},{\"/getcar\":\"car\"}]   //模拟数据get的地址:数据源文件\n     },\n    root:\"./\",          //服务器根目录，默认 \"./\"\n    ext:\".html\",        //服务器需要渲染的页面模板后缀，默认\".html\"\n    mockBase:\"./mock\"   //mock数据的json文件存放目录，默认\"./\"\n};\n```\n##2,创建mock文件\n在第一步的mockBase配置的目录下创建数据源json文件\n[也可以是其他格式的文件，内容也可以不是json格式，获取数据源的时候检测不是标准json会在控制台输出警告，\n不会影响正常使用]，\n\n##3,创建html页面\n根据第一步配置的ext后缀名称创建页面，然后正常ajax请求配置好的url即可\n如：\n```\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n\t$(function(){\n\t\t $.get(\"/getinfo\",function(data){\n\t\t\t\tconsole.log(data);\n\t\t\t})\n\t})\n</script>\n```\n\n启动服务器 \n```\nhttp-server-cli\n```\n\n","created":"2015-04-27T14:05:51.449Z","modified":"2015-04-28T06:35:52.356Z","lastPublisher":{"name":"yeanzhi","email":"807754634@qq.com"},"owners":[{"name":"yeanzhi","email":"807754634@qq.com"}],"other":{"_attachments":{},"_from":".","_id":"http-server-cli","_nodeVersion":"0.12.0","_npmUser":{"name":"yeanzhi","email":"807754634@qq.com"},"_npmVersion":"2.5.1","_rev":"1-0b3381f3b06cb522bbe56a9960f69f02","_shasum":"e0ce7547c3710cd978c29c92c9f4655859515fad","directories":{},"dist-tags":{"latest":"0.2.1"},"dist":{"shasum":"e0ce7547c3710cd978c29c92c9f4655859515fad","tarball":"http://registry.npmjs.org/http-server-cli/-/http-server-cli-0.2.1.tgz"},"maintainers":[{"name":"yeanzhi","email":"807754634@qq.com"}],"readmeFilename":"README.md","time":{"modified":"2015-04-28T06:35:52.356Z","created":"2015-04-27T14:05:51.449Z","0.1.0":"2015-04-27T14:05:51.449Z","0.1.1":"2015-04-27T14:18:55.774Z","0.1.2":"2015-04-27T14:25:39.796Z","0.1.3":"2015-04-27T14:30:20.181Z","0.1.4":"2015-04-27T14:32:15.259Z","0.1.5":"2015-04-27T16:05:33.163Z","0.1.6":"2015-04-27T16:43:02.287Z","0.1.7":"2015-04-28T02:21:43.010Z","0.2.0":"2015-04-28T02:34:44.610Z","0.2.1":"2015-04-28T06:35:52.356Z"}}}